title: Jaime Harrison
added: Harrison ultimately lost the election to Lindsey Graham by over ten percentage points, garnering 44.2% of the vote compared to Graham's 54.5%.<ref>[https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/03/south-carolina-senate-election-results-2020-433581 Graham fends off Harrison in South Carolina Senate race] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117025426/https://www.politico.com/news/2020/11/03/south-carolina-senate-election-results-2020-433581 |date=November 17, 2020 }}, ''[[Politico]]'', November 3, 2020.</ref>
